examples.en: Jealousy is a vice.

examples.en: Music is the only sensual pleasure without vice.

examples.en: Galileo was condemned as a heretic for supporting Copernicus's thesis that the earth revolves around the sun and not vice versa.

examples.en: When the president died the vice president was chosen to head the firm.

examples.en: She was named to replace him as the company's vice president.

examples.en: He moved up through the ranks to become vice president of the company.

examples.en: He became the Vice President of the United States.

examples.en: Her title of vice president had been nominal only.

examples.en: The duties of the club's vice president are inconsiderable by any standard.
